Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
init_ignore_pg...polarity_check(25.10)  init_ignore_pg...polarity_check(25.10)

Name
       init_ignore_pgpin_polarity_check

Syntax
       init_ignore_pgpin_polarity_check

       Type: String

       Default: NULL

       Specifies  space separated list of leaf cell pin names to ignore polar-
       ity checking during globalNetConnect, 1801  UPF,  and  CPF  operations.
       Allows  USE  POWER  pin  to  be  connected to a USE GROUND net (or vice
       versa).

       When specified, GNC/CPF are allowed to silently make connections to  PG
       pins  that are not of the same polarity as the PG net that they are be-
       ing connected to. The list of pin names is only checked  for  the  case
       where  a polarity check failed and then can be ignored and connected in
       spite of the polarity mismatch.

Example
       set init_ignore_pgpin_polarity_check "bias"

